</b></p>
<p><b>the immediate cease-fire. 
</b></p>
<p><b> 
</b></p>
<p><b>Within the context of the Disarmament, Demobilization 
and Reintegration program, 23670 combatants have 
been registered and disarmed in north and South 
Sudan. 2690 individuals have been re-integrated in 
South-Kordofan, 2780 in Blue Nile State and 1177 in 
