Women from Gender-Based Violence was held in El 
Fasher. 40 senior government officials representing 
various government offices, including the Wali&#8217;s 
Advisors, Minister for Agriculture, Director for Public 
Service, Dir-Gen of the Ministry of Social Affairs, 
Director of the Ministry of Health, Director of the El 
Fasher hospital, the State Legal Consultant, Ministry of 
Education. 
 
