witnesses and victims of human rights violations, that witnesses and victims are not 
subjected to any violence, reprisals or harassment due to their cooperation with 
human rights monitors; and that all necessary and feasible measures are taken to 
protect witnesses and victims against violence, reprisals and harassment by third 
parties.  
