</p>
<p>Ten Darfur activists including human rights lawyers 
were arrested and detained in Khartoum from 30 
October to 2010 13 January 2011(7 released), 16 
January (2 released) and 21 January (1 released), 
leaving three others in detention. On 23 January 2011, 
HRS met with four of them after their release by 
NISS. 
</p>
