<p><b>  1.6.2 Remove restrictions in the National Press Laws that can be used to threaten the 
work and independence of journalists acting as human rights defenders and bring 
them into line with the Interim Constitution, the International Covenant on Civil and 
Political Rights and other applicable international standards. 
</b></p>
