and ensuring access for human rights defenders to this information. Ensure the 
effective functioning of documentation centres within the human rights units of the 
Ministries of the Interior, Defence, Welfare and others. 
</b></p>
<p>Mid-term 
</p>
<p>&#8226; Systems in place and documentation centres functioning effectively 
</p>
